Class InternshipWithdrawalApplicant

java.lang.Object
InternshipWithdrawalApplicant
public class InternshipWithdrawalApplicant extends Object
Represents a student applying to withdraw from an accepted internship. Tracks the student, the associated internship, and a unique ID.
